<p>Overnight Russian missile and drone strikes struck Kyiv and other parts of Ukraine early on October 26, 2025, killing at least three people in the capital and wounding dozens, officials said . Ukrainian authorities reported intense damage to residential buildings and fires in multiple districts while the air force said it had shot down large numbers of incoming weapons as the city sheltered residents . The strikes came amid renewed appeals from President Volodymyr Zelenskiy for stronger air defences and expanded sanctions against Russia .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/tV9CV2ArE35yBtuS9m7krqnAeZvN5ytE1P_WZ_6VtYeXPsjTr443FLZk_Rbqz6rxqyw9iJXqx3xaBW_zURKqdUDB62HmVdZ1AWdRC0jB' alt='A firefighting helicopter drops water over food warehouses struck by a missile near Kyiv after overnight attacks' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Scale of attack: Ukraine said Moscow fired Iskander ballistic missiles and dozens of attack drones in the overnight raids, claiming it downed four ballistic missiles and about 50 drones .</li><li>Damage footprint: Fires broke out and at least three apartment complexes were damaged in Kyiv’s Desnyansky and Darnytsky districts, prompting large-scale emergency response efforts .</li><li>Civilian toll details: Among those wounded in Kyiv were children; the mayor said six children were hurt in the overnight attack .</li><li>Political response: Western allies this week announced new sanctions targeting Russian energy, and Ukraine’s president renewed calls for long‑range weapons and tougher measures against Moscow .</li></ul><blockquote>Remain in shelters - Head of Kyiv&#x27;s military administration</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Vitali Klitschko, mayor of Kyiv: Klitschko reported children among the wounded and described fires in apartment buildings while urging residents to follow safety orders. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/czxnye07x2lo'>BBC</a>)</li><li>Volodymyr Zelenskiy, president of Ukraine: Zelenskiy called for new strong sanctions and appealed to Western partners for long‑range missiles and expanded air‑defence support. (<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2025/oct/25/russian-overnight-strikes-ukraine-zelenskyy-sanctions-oil'>The Guardian</a>)</li><li>United States and European Union: Officials in Washington and Brussels announced new sanctions this week that target Russian energy exports as part of pressure on Moscow. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1951322/russian-strikes-on-ukraine-kill-four'>Dawn</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/comments/1ogdx1t/deadly_russian_strikes_tear_into_kyiv_residential/'>Deadly Russian strikes tear into Kyiv residential high-rises in second attack within 24 hours | CNN</a> - reddit.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/russia-drone-attack-on-kyiv-ukraine-october-death-toll-26-2025/article70204299.ece'>Russian drone attack kills three in Kyiv: Mayor</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/ukraine-russian-missile-drone-attacks-kyiv-dnipropetrovsk/'>At least 4 killed in Ukraine after Russian missile and drone attacks</a> - cbsnews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/3-dead-29-wounded-in-kyiv-after-russia-strikes-ukrainian-capital-9519580#publisher=newsstand'>3 Dead, 29 Wounded In Kyiv After Russia Strikes Ukrainian Capital</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/czxnye07x2lo'>Three killed in Russian strikes on Kyiv, officials say</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/26/russian-overnight-attack-on-ukraines-kyiv-kills-at-least-3-wounds-dozens'>Russian overnight attack on Ukraine’s Kyiv kills at least 3, wounds dozens</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/Russian-attack-on-Kyiv-kills-three-injures-31-including-6-children-Ukraine-says'>Russian attack on Kyiv kills three, injures 31, including 6 children, Ukraine says</a